{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_530.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x17,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Now, today we will be cooking a stew."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I like stew, although I specialize in eating them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It's easy to cook and you get to use a variety of ingredients."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Plus, even if you make a mistake in the middle, you can still redeem it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "How reassuring! That is the perfect dish for me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Then, let's start. First fill the pot with water and drop in the meat ingredients."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x11,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Meat ingredients...understood. Then I shall drop in the frogs and lizards that I brought..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hold it right there! You can't use frogs or lizards!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Do you not like frogs? Their texture is similar to chicken, and they are really delicious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Then let's just use chicken!<CR>Just...say no to frogs and lizards!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "What about newts?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Uhhh, that's a no, too...<CR>Sorry, but please use the<CR>ingredients I've prepared."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Understood. I will simply follow your directions, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Oookay, it's done! How is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Its appearance is drastically different from the stews I usually eat."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "The size of the ingredients are all different, and most of all, the color of the soup looks bad..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "It's pretty good for your first time. Now, you just have to get used to it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "The seasoning is done perfectly, so I'm sure it'll taste good when you eat it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "When making stews, it's always better to make bigger portions."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "The ingredients will mix together more, giving the stew more depth of flavor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "The more you make, the better it will taste... That is very useful information."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "So, I just have to make an overwhelming amount!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "(It went pretty well this time...I think.)"
        }
    ]
}